### Rick & Morty Platform - Test de Nuevas Funcionalidades
### Archivo para usar con REST Client (VS Code Extension) o Thunder Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### 1. HEALTH CHECK
### ============================================

GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ============================================
### 2. PERSONAJES - Búsqueda Avanzada
### ============================================

### Listar todos los personajes
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filtrar por estado y especie
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters?status=alive&species=Human
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filtrar con múltiples parámetros y ordenamiento
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters?status=alive&gender=female&sort=-name
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar personajes por texto
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters/search?q=morty
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener estadísticas de personajes
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Exportar personajes a JSON
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters/export?format=json&status=alive
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Exportar personajes a CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters/export?format=csv
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Exportar personajes a Excel
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters/export?format=excel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 3. FAVORITOS - CRUD Completo
### ============================================

### Listar favoritos con paginación
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filtrar favoritos por tipo
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites?resourceType=character&sort=-createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar en favoritos
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/search?q=rick
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener estadísticas de favoritos
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Agregar a favoritos
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceType": "character",
  "resourceId": 1,
  "notes": "Rick Sanchez - Mi personaje favorito"
}

### Obtener un favorito específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/YOUR_FAVORITE_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Actualizar favorito
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/favorites/YOUR_FAVORITE_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Rick Sanchez - Actualizado"
}

### Eliminar favorito
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/favorites/YOUR_FAVORITE_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Exportar favoritos a CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/export?format=csv
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Exportar favoritos a Excel
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/export?format=excel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 4. ARCHIVOS - Gestión Completa
### ============================================

### Listar archivos con paginación
GET {{baseUrl}}/files?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filtrar archivos por categoría
GET {{baseUrl}}/files?category=documentos&sort=-createdAt
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar archivos
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/search?q=documento
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener estadísticas de archivos
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Subir un archivo (usa Postman/Thunder Client para esto)
### POST {{baseUrl}}/files/upload
### Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### Content-Type: multipart/form-data
### 
### file: [seleccionar archivo]
### description: "Descripción del archivo"
### category: "documentos"

### Descargar archivo
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/YOUR_FILE_ID/download
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Eliminar archivo
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/files/YOUR_FILE_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 5. UBICACIONES - Filtros Avanzados
### ============================================

### Listar ubicaciones
GET {{baseUrl}}/locations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filtrar ubicaciones
GET {{baseUrl}}/locations?name=Earth
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 6. EPISODIOS - Filtros Avanzados
### ============================================

### Listar episodios
GET {{baseUrl}}/episodes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filtrar episodios
GET {{baseUrl}}/episodes?name=Pilot
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### TESTS DE VALIDACIÓN
### ============================================

### Error: Validación de favorito (falta resourceType)
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resourceId": 1
}

### Error: Validación de paginación (página negativa)
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites?page=-1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Error: Límite excedido
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites?limit=200
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### TESTS DE EXPORTACIÓN
### ============================================

### Exportar personajes filtrados a Excel
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters/export?format=excel&status=alive&species=Human
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Exportar favoritos a CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/export?format=csv
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### TESTS DE ORDENAMIENTO
### ============================================

### Ordenar favoritos por fecha (más recientes primero)
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites?sort=-createdAt&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Ordenar archivos por tamaño (mayores primero)
GET {{baseUrl}}/files?sort=-size
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### TESTS DE BÚSQUEDA
### ============================================

### Buscar personajes
GET {{baseUrl}}/characters/search?q=morty&page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar favoritos
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites/search?q=rick&page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar archivos
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/search?q=documento
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
